<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='974000' id='t-974000'>to help the world.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='976000' id='t-976000'>And so that's why I think, personally, that toys can change the world.</span>
</span>
</p>
